```plantuml
@startuml domingo1021_Bunny-code

actor User
participant "Web Application" as WebApp
participant "Nginx Reverse Proxy" as Nginx
participant "Express Backend" as Backend
participant "MySQL Database" as MySQL
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "InfluxDB" as InfluxDB
participant "Docker Sandbox" as Sandbox
participant "Socket.IO" as SocketIO
participant "S3 Storage" as S3
participant "CloudFront CDN" as CloudFront
participant "CloudWatch" as CloudWatch

User -> WebApp: Access Code Platform
WebApp -> Nginx: HTTP Request
Nginx -> Backend: Route Request
Backend -> Redis: Check Cache for User Session
Redis -> Backend: Session Data
Backend -> MySQL: Query User Data
MySQL -> Backend: User Data
Backend -> S3: Retrieve Code Files
S3 -> Backend: Code Files
Backend -> CloudFront: Deliver Static Content
CloudFront -> User: Static Content
Backend -> SocketIO: Establish WebSocket Connection
SocketIO -> User: Real-time Updates
User -> WebApp: Start Coding Battle
WebApp -> Backend: Initiate Battle Request
Backend -> Sandbox: Execute Code in Docker
Sandbox -> Backend: Execution Results
Backend -> InfluxDB: Log Coding Activity
InfluxDB -> Backend: Activity Logs
Backend -> Redis: Update Battle Status
Backend -> CloudWatch: Send Logs and Metrics
CloudWatch -> Backend: Monitoring Data

@enduml
```